The paper discusses the visualization and interpretation of deep neural networks, specifically convolutional neural networks (convnets), in the context of image recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the training of DNNs, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the progress in the field, which is related to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The regularization methods introduced in the paper are related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the interpretation of the visualizations, which is related to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
